/* ************************************************************************** */
/*
   METHOD:         Constructor for a XNFmsgclass object
   DESCRIPTION:
   DEPENDENCIES:
   DEPENDED ON BY:
   INPUT PARAMS:
   OUTPUT PARAMS:  NONE
   RETURN VALUE:   NONE
   CONSTANTS:      NONE
   VARIABLES:      NONE
